parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected deployment of airbags can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the distraction and loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbag deployment without any impact or collision
airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
sudden and unexpected explosion of the airbag.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the SRS control unit can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to unexpected airbag deployment or failure to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: SRS light illuminates on the dashboard
failure to deploy airbags in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause unexpected airbag deployment or failure to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
failure to deploy airbags in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to dangerous situations, especially when driving at high speeds or carrying passengers.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or dies while driving
the engine shuts off without warning
the ignition switch feels loose or worn out
the key gets stuck in the ignition
or the ignition switch needs to be jiggled to start the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a fire, leading to a hazardous situation for the occupants and other road users.
symptoms: especially in the electrical wiring or door panel
the power window switch assembly melts
the plastic door latch mechanism is damaged
and the smoke from the fire fills the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The ABS warning light on the dashboard comes on and stays on
the ABS system improperly engages at low speeds on dry pavement
the brake pedal goes to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The SRS light on the dashboard comes on and stays on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic lock system can cause the locks to malfunction, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The power locks lock uncontrollably and drain the battery
the electronic lock unit needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the counter balance shaft seal can cause sudden and rapid oil loss, leading to engine damage, stalling, or even complete engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of the cam shaft seal can cause oil leakage, which can lead to engine damage, stalling, or even complete engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: oil saturation of the timing belt

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air bag control module can cause the air bag system to malfunction, leading to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: failure to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs at high speed or in heavy traffic.
